Whether you live in Tokyo or not, anyone can submit an image to be considered
for Tokyo Camera Club's feed, as long as the photo is of someplace in Japan.
Rules, in English, for how to submit a photo can be found
[here](https://www.facebook.com/camera.jpn/app/354489587970057/).

More Tokyo Camera Club photographs can be seen on
[Instagram](https://www.instagram.com/tokyocameraclub/), Twitter,
[Facebook](https://www.facebook.com/camera.jpn/) and [on the
web](http://tokyocameraclub.com/photos/editors.php).

